{"tid":947221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4港男遊日本 咖啡店齋坐近句鐘   網民：影衰晒","createTime":"2018-12-19T06:19:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T04:26:38.000Z","uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":139,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"fffabcca69367d260d48e9bb89bd20ca6c52b898","tid":947221,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:19:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xa0bbW_L0TflZYU_vK89jw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/b8faa9867bfe179ca5eb8e78e676b553\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fxa0bbW_L0TflZYU_vK89jw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fb8faa9867bfe179ca5eb8e78e676b553&h=657e306f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本是一個注重禮儀的國家，但不時有自私港人作出一些失禮行為，惹怒日人。近日有港人衝入日本一間咖啡店斟水，甚至坐下玩手機大半小時，惹來網民直斥︰「搞搞震，無幫襯」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民星期二（18日）在討論區發貼，指日前在日本札幌新千歳機場的一間主題咖啡店用餐，誰知突然有4名操粵語男子走入餐廳︰「喂！呢度有水斟喎，唔使錢㗎，入去囉」。<br />\n<br />\n發貼者指，該4名男子一字排開，佔據了一行座位，「然後個個都去自助飲水機攞杯裝水，裝完水飲就拎手機出嚟玩」。他表示，雖然當時店員眼望望，但沒有出聲阻止，「過咗大約大半個鐘，佢哋飲夠玩夠之後，就施施然咁走人，乜都無幫襯」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民不齒四人所為，批評他們：「影衰晒」、「無修養」，又指他們「唔係窮，而係貪小便宜」。"},{"pid":"f758a94bc545ba30fde2b05807292dcd2dbf4fc9","tid":947221,"uid":201374,"like":185,"dislike":3,"score":182,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:20:58.000Z","msg":"冇咗疊YEN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87dd92b830909d37abb1dfacf7ee322ef1be504","tid":947221,"uid":31200,"like":81,"dislike":8,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:22:49.000Z","msg":"香港D店員會走埋黎黑面+扔個餐牌黎問你飲咩"},{"pid":"19c68df34f30e159afeb5c35a14d2c0c2e3f5eeb","tid":947221,"uid":1251,"like":163,"dislike":4,"score":159,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"仲以為係啲師奶<br />\n男人老狗都咁撚cheap<br />\n影衰晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/f